                {
                    "id": "default_run_1hour",
                    "description": "One-hour integration under the S&P Chapter 5 mid-stratosphere defaults (T=227 K, M=3.1e23 m^-3, ~30 km). Shows the coupled evolution of the ozone reservoir and the NOx / HOx / ClOx / BrOx catalytic radical pools that destroy it.",
